http://symptomresearch.nih.gov

   The Symptom Research interactive clinical research textbook contains
   over 20 chapters on different aspects of clinical pain and symptom
   research. Pain Research, Analgesia, Neuralgia, Headache, Causalgia,
   Delirium, Care for the dying, Prognostication, Fatigue, Anorexia,
   Cachexia, Insomnia, Nausea, Dyspnea, Hospice, Epidemiology,
   Constipation, Clinical pain

